\f0\b\fs44 \cf0 I love the 90\'92s\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Week 3 \'96 Recipe for Progress\
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 ME\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Welcome to everyone and the online community\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Last was some decisions made during a time of success that ultimately lead to financial failure.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What we said was there were specific things you can do to ruin your life\'85and since no one wants to do that you should do the opposite.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This week I want to talk to you about a decision that was made during the 90\'92s in a season of chaos and financial ruin that has lead to extreme success even to this day.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 	\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 (graphic showing Apple\'92s stock growth)\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  Many of us today would love to have that sort of progress in our personal lives, financial lives, spiritual lives, etc\'85The problem is for many of us we believe that it is our desire that will drive progress in our lives.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I know this because I\'92ve said things like:\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92m serious this time\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I promise\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I really want to\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}As if our emotional response to a situation has any bearing on where we end up in life.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  When we can remove that lie from our thinking it allows us to be open to what really causes progress in our lives\'85\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\fs28 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Change precedes progress\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1
\fs24 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Everyone wants progress, but few people are willing to make the change.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}People want to lose weight but they aren\'92t really willing to change eating habits\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}People want to be financially more secure but refuse to change spending habits\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}People want relational health but few people will change what type of person they keep as close friends\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:  So today I want to look at what apple did and I believe we can learn from that as seek have real progress in our lives\'85\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Change in leadership\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs18 \cf5 \super 46\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Why do you call me, \'91Lord, Lord,\'92\'a0and do not do what I say?\'a0Luke 6:46\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is a way to live life that appears to be good but deep down your heart is far from God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When was the last time you did what Jesus said\'85to you\'85and you only?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s so easy to point to things you either already overcame or don\'92t struggle with.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you\'92re a Christian I have a different question for you\'85\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Why are you here if all you\'92re going to do is ignore what God says and then go off and do whatever you want?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Last question:  What is it that you know God is calling you to do that you are fighting?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you are serious about progress in your life \'96 there has to be a change in leadership!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If He isn\'92t Lord of all, He isn\'92t Lord at all!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf3 Transition:  Because, with a change in leadership comes two more things.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Change in Direction\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Apple went from designing a whole bunch of things and with the goal of profit in mind to designing very few things but with quality and focus in mind\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For us as Christians here is how Paul puts it\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 12\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Therefore, brothers and sisters, we have an obligation\'97but it is not to the flesh, to live according to it.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 13\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For if you live according to the flesh, you will die;\'a0but if by the Spirit you put to death the misdeeds of the body,\'a0you will live.  
\f2\b\fs18 \super 14\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub For those who are led by the Spirit of God\'a0are the children of God.\'a0  Romans 8:12-14\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You have an obligation\'85there is no better word.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is not a suggestion or gentle nudge\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is a responsibility to follow and in turn change directions.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God\'92s Spirit is there to lead you into a new direction\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You only get to hear that though by listening!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}QUESTION \'96 When was the last time you carved out time for God to speak to you\'85not the other way around?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \'93Again, you can\'92t connect the dots looking forward; you can only connect them looking backwards.  So you have to trust that the dots will somehow connect in your future.  You have to trust in something \'96 your gut, destiny, life, karma, whatever.  This approach has never let me down, and it has made all the difference in my life.\'94  Steve Jobs\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For us a Christians we don\'92t believe in karma or anything like that but I find it amazing his perspective on connecting the dots.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You can\'92t fix the problems you are not aware of\'85so you have to listen and be mindful of what God is saying to you.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf3 Transition:  And when you change your direction all of us sudden the last thing happens\'85\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Change in perspective\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Steve Jobs changed the perspective of this company immediately\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He knew that the type of thinking that had gotten them to where they were was not going to be what got them to where they needed to be.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 Show clip of the commercial he launched 10 weeks after arriving\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We don\'92t need to change what we think as much as how we see the world we live in and what our place is in it!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 9\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But you are a chosen people,\'a0a royal priesthood,\'a0a holy nation,\'a0God\'92s special possession,\'a0that you may declare the praises of him who called you out of darkness into his wonderful light.
\f2\b\fs18 \super 10\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Once you were not a people, but now you are the people of God;\'a0once you had not received mercy, but now you have received mercy.\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 11\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Dear friends,\'a0I urge you, as foreigners and exiles,\'a0to abstain from sinful desires,\'a0which wage war against your soul.  1 Peter 2\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf3 Transition:\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Read the book of Mark this week \'96 it is roughly 4 chapters a day\'85you can do it!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This encompasses all three areas of your life and while there may be some unique steps you need to make in light of today this is universal step I want all of us to make.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 WE\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf7 Illustration of me telling Claire she is a world changer and her looking at me and innocently asking me why does the world need to be changed?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Claire doesn\'92t see it yet.  She will one day.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When we see as God see\'92s we will do as God says!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can you imagine for a second how different your life would be if over the next year you really believed Change Precedes Progress and consistently made the changes you know you needed to make?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
